com.wx.properties.property

Class BufferedProperty<Type>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wx.properties.property.Property<Type>
      • com.wx.properties.property.BufferedProperty<Type>
  • Type Parameters:
    Type - Type of the property

    public class BufferedProperty<Type>
extends Property<Type>
    Simple implementation of the property that will wrap another property and buffer its value.

    This can be useful for properties that are accessed a lot and have a read/write cost.

    Date: Oct 10, 2013
